nodes.text: An office tower on Coruscant was owned by the Trade Federation during the Clone Wars. During the plot to assassinate Senator Amidala, bounty hunter Zam Wesell used this building as her outpost while her ASN-121 assassin droid traveled to the Senator's apartment. When the plot was foiled, Wesell shot her droid—which was carrying Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi—from the roof.
